<h2 id="google-analytics">Google Analytics</h2>

<p>Specify <code class="highlighter-rouge">ga_analytics</code> in your <code class="highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> and restart the server to add Google Analytics tracking code.</p>

<div class="language-ruby highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># Google Analytics example</span>
<span class="ss">ga_analytics: </span><span class="no">UA</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mo">000000</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">0</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

